  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the speculaas spice mix and sauté for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Stir in the lentils and rice and coat them with oil and spices for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and coconut milk and bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes or until lentils are tender and rice is cooked.",
    "Stir in the nuka-pickle concentrate and season with salt to taste.",
    "Remove from heat, let stand covered for 5 minutes, then fluff with a fork.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley.",
    "Enjoy your indulgent brunch pilaf!"
